? What does the first law of thermodynamics state?
[A] Heat cannot flow from a cold body to a hot body spontaneously
[B]* Energy cannot be created or destroyed, only converted from one form to another
[C] The entropy of an isolated system always increases over time
[D] At absolute zero, the entropy of a perfect crystal is zero
